Author: Hairless_Human
Text: Me a soup lover: 1500 cals is about 12 cans of progresso light soup (a 120 cal can). Would I be able to fit 12 cans in me. No. I don't think anyone could. Is that A LOT of sodium? Yes. Do I care? No. My record is 4 and I thought I was gonna burst and plus side I was still at a deficit. Sorry I like seeing how many cans of soup can fit into someones cal budget/TDEE.
